# 🎬 MovieSpace

MovieSpace is a responsive React-based web application that allows users to search for movies using the OMDb API.

It provides details such as title, year, poster, and type (movie/series).


---

## 🚀 Live Demo: https://movie-space-dggk.vercel.app/  


## 🌟 Features

- 🔍 Search movies by title
- 📅 Display movie year and type (movie/series/episode)
- 🖼️ Poster image preview
- ⚡ Fast and responsive UI
- 🔑 Powered by the OMDb API



